</p></span></li><li><img src="http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7303/16355291316_d49d50fce9.jpg" title="IMG_7472" alt=""  /><span class="caption"><p>IMG_7472</p></span></li><li><img src="http://farm9.staticflickr.com/8667/16194632889_98c1b0582f.jpg" title="Perth Australia Day Skyshow 2015" alt=""  /><span class="caption"><p>Perth Australia Day Skyshow 2015</p></span></li><li><img src="http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7305/16193238908_91fd57c9d1.jpg" title="Perth Australia Day Skyshow 2015" alt=""  /><span class="caption"><p>Perth Australia Day Skyshow 2015</p></span></li><li><img src="http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7448/16193468580_79d9ee9ccd.jpg" title="Perth Australia Day Skyshow 2015" alt=""  /><span class="caption"><p>Perth Australia Day Skyshow 2015</p></span></li><li><img src="http://farm9.staticflickr.com/8668/16379959225_bbff1b05a0.jpg" title="Australia Day Fireworks" alt=""  /><span class="caption"><p>Australia Day Fireworks</p></span></li><li><img src="http://farm9.staticflickr.com/8634/16376686042_bef5785344.jpg" title="Australia Day fireworks" alt=""  /><span class="caption"><p>Australia Day fireworks</p></span></li><li><img src="http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7286/16350684356_714f406b48.jpg" title="IMG_2989.jpg" alt=""  /><span class="caption"><p>IMG_2989.jpg</p></span></li><li><img src="http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7365/16185807529_f4e26850fc.jpg" title="DSC_6063" alt=""  /><span class="caption"><p>DSC_6063</p></span></li><li><img src="http://farm9.staticflickr.com/8621/16185808409_f2b7f8b8ba.jpg" title="DSC_6035" alt=""  /><span class="caption"><p>DSC_6035</p></span></li><li><img src="http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7414/15752044563_9a59a61750.jpg" title="DSC_6002" alt=""  /><span class="caption"><p>DSC_6002</p></span></li></ul></div><div style="clear:both"></div></div></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="http://www.slickrflickr.com/2892/new-mobile-responsive-slideshow/">New mobile responsive slideshow</a> which can be activated by setting <code>responsive="on"</code> on each <i>slickr-flickr</i> command or by setting the <i>Mobile responsive</i> option on the Slickr Flickr settings page</li>\n<li>Updated to Galleria 1.4.2 which allows multiple gallerias per page with different themes (skins), For example, you probably want to use the <i>classic</i> theme for your small gallerias in the sidebars and maybe <i>folio</i>, <i>miniml</i> or <i>azur</i> or <twelve> as the theme for the featured gallery in the main section of the page</li>\n<li>Added <i>class</i> parameter to make it easy to wrap text around a slideshow. For example, this page has a slideshow with <code>class="alignright"</code></li>\n<li><i>flickr_link_target</i> parameter now works on Galleria so your link to the photo can open a new tab or window</li>\n<li>fix to Flickr RSS URLs</li>\n<li>fix bug with original size photos</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:64:"http://www.slickrflickr.com/2906/slickr-flickr-2-3-release/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:1:"p";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:12:"Updated by .";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:5:{s:2:"id";s:23:"authorsure-last-updated";s:5:"class";s:13:"updated right";s:9:"itemscope";s:9:"itemscope";s:8:"itemtype";s:25:"http://schema.org/WebPage";s:6:"itemid";s:59:"http://www.slickrflickr.com/2906/slickr-flickr-2-3-release/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"span";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:5:"style";s:10:"float:none";s:5:"class";s:12:"author vcard";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_bas