(4864, 861, 'layout_content_0_block_0_content', 'Els nanos i gegants de Vinaròs no faltarem a la trobada de Benicàssim, enguany amb alguns canvis respecte les trobades anteriors, pode afirmar que van fer una cercavila nocturna a la que no estem acostumats, però com som uns “todo-terrenos” enseguida ens acostumaren a  la novetat. Benicàssim, moltíssima gent pels carrers i molt animats!!!\r\n\r\n<a href="http://dev.nanosigegants.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8935.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-864" alt="IMG_8935" src="http://dev.nanosigegants.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8935-610x406.jpg" width="610" height="406" /></a> <a href="http://dev.nanosigegants.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8963.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-865" alt="IMG_8963" src="http://dev.nanosigegants.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8963-610x406.jpg" width="610" height="406" /></a> <a href="http://dev.nanosigegants.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8972.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-866" alt="IMG_8972" src="http://dev.nanosigegants.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8972-333x500.jpg" width="333" height="500" /></a> <a href="http://dev.nanosigegants.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8973.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-867" alt="IMG_8973" src="http://dev.nanosigegants.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8973-610x406.jpg" width="610" height="406" /></a> <a href="http://dev.nanosigegants.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8975.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-868" alt="IMG_8975" src="http://dev.nanosigegants.com/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8975-333x500.jpg" width="333" height="500" /></a>'),
